  "translations": {
    "en": "Ali b. Ahmad b. Abdullah b. Ahmad b. Abi Abdillah al-Barqi narrated to us. He said: My father narrated to me from his grandfather Ahmad b. Abi Abdillah. He said: My father narrated to us from Ali b. al-Nu'man from Fadl b. Yunus from Abdullah b. Sinan. He said: Abu Abdillah al-Sadiq (peace be upon him) said:",
